title: 2022 CFB Pick Em Week 4
description:
Dave, Big Cat & Rico are back for Week 4 of the CFB season. Big Cat & Dave recap their hectic weekend in Vegas where their friendship almost ended. Also what everyone's been waiting for, is this the week Rico cracks into the top 20 bloggers?


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
